title: the lakes
description:
It's time to break down the bonus track for Folklore. What inspired Taylor for this song? It's pretty dark, but she poetically ties it all together in a beautiful way.
What did we miss? What else would you like to hear from us? And who is ready for Midnights? It's almost here, and we have some listening party plans! Be sure to join us on Instagram, TikTok and locally, at the Texican Court this Saturday! Details are posted on the socials- @the13Podcast.
Hit us up anytime!
